- cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) is relevant as the paper discusses the challenges of matching computation and communication complexity in Internet-based systems. 
- cs.SE (Software Engineering) is relevant as the paper covers programming tools for parallel programming. 
- cs.PL (Programming Languages) is less likely but still possible as the paper discusses programming tools and models for parallel computing.
